${voffset 10}${color EAEAEA}${font GE Inspira:pixelsize=120}${time %H:%M:%S}${font}
${voffset 4}${offset 200}${color FFA300}${font GE Inspira:pixelsize=42}${time %d} ${voffset -15}${color EAEAEA}${font GE Inspira:pixelsize=22}${time  %B} ${time %Y}${font}${voffset 24}${font GE Inspira:pixelsize=58}${offset -220}${time %A}${font}
